In the INTEREST OF N.S. and M.S., Minor Children, M.S., Father, Appellant, P.A., Mother, Appellant. No. 19-0533 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 5, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother appeals the termination of her parental rights to two children, and a father appeals the termination of his parental rights to the older child. AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.
